{"id": "naos012", "name": "Audio_Velvet_698_11_19", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["UV_Bar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-V]"], "content": "<i>That's it for tonight's performance! Thank you for coming!</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "Audience cheers"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Xenon was so cool! That performance was so good!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "No kidding~\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Ah, the bus service is almost ending. We better get moving.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Ummm... NEKO wants to stay here a bit longer. Linda-chan, you can go back first.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Eh? This place will become a bar very soon...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO will leave before 12:00 am, so no need to worry~\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Alright... be careful yourself. If you wander around outside past midnight, drones and law enforcement agents will start to harass you.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "I know, I know~\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Hi, milk.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bartender"], "content": "Gotcha.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Hellloo! Mister pervert!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... You again?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "What? Why the distasteful look!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Because every time I run into you, I get caught up in some random crap.\nWhat are you doing here at this time? Aren't you afraid of being caught?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO was here to see you perform!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...... Eh?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "You're Xenon, right? On top of that! You were also Simon from CP! NEKO knew it! No wonder your face seemed so familiar!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bartender"], "content": "Haha, getting recognized by fans again? Told ya; with that long hair of yours, the helmet won't do a thing.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Shut up... so what if I am? It's not like I'm going out of my way to hide this information.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "WOW! Right on the money! This is not public knowledge yet, isn't it? That Simon is Xenon! This is big news!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It's not that big of a reveal... Also, keep your voice down...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Why didn't you just continue using the name \"Simon\"? Your music will be so much more popular! Right now, your popularity is not even half of what CP used to have.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... CP has already disbanded. The public has too many imaginations about it that are not related to music. I want a complete restart; a simple focus on music alone. That's all.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bartender"], "content": "This bulls*** reasoning again...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "He~? Is this the reason behind the disbandment?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bartender"], "content": "Haha... Little girl, just give up. He's not gonna talk.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Who you calling little girl!? NEKO is already 16!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... On a side note, that cat last time, what happened afterward?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Ah, it's still in NEKO's room... But NEKO's house doesn't have a pet registration, and there's someone who's allergic to cats... Right now, I'm pretty much just raising it in secret. So troublesome~~~\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... I do know someone who might be able to adopt it, but that dude already has a dog...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Really!? Can you please ask him?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Alright. I'll ask.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "You're my savior~ Or else NEKO's gonna get busted by my family anytime soon...\nLet's exchange iM so we can better communicate with each other!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sure.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imlike", "iM exchange"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Yeah~ Xenon's iM get!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Don't send it to some random stranger.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "No worries, I won't! NEKO is very good at keeping secrets~ Oh, and NEKO won't spill the secret that Xenon is Simon as well!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Aren't you spilling it right now...?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["UV_Bar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-V]"], "content": "<i>今日はこれで終わり！ありがとう！</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "観客の歓声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Xenonまじかっこよすぎ！あ～今日もよかった！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "ほんとだよ～\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "あ、もうこんな時間だ。急ぐか。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "うん……NEKOもう少しここに残るね。\nLindaっち先に帰ってて！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "え？\nここそろそろバーになる時間だけど……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKOも12時前には帰るからさ！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "分かったけど……気を付けなよ。\n夜中に外にいると、ドローンと執法員に目つけられるよ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "分かってる分かってる～\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "牛乳で。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["バーテンダー"], "content": "はい。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "やっほ！痴漢さん！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……またお前か。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "何その顔～すごい嫌そうな顔！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……お前に会うと、ろくなことがない。\nこんな時間にここで何してる？\n捕まりたいのか？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKOあなたのライブ見に来たんだ！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……え？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Xenonでしょ？あと！CPのSimonもおにーさんでしょ？\n顔に見覚えあるなーってNEKOずっと思ってたんだよね！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["バーテンダー"], "content": "ははは、ファンに見破られてしまいましたね。\n髪を伸ばして、ヘルメットなんてしても意味ないって言ったでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "うるさいな……バレたからなんだ。\n別にハナから隠そうと思ってない。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "わー！やっぱり！？\nこのこと知ってる人あんまりいないんでしょ？\nSimonはXenon！ビッグニュースだー！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別に大したことじゃないだろ。\nそれより、声デカい……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "なんでSimonの名前でやらないの？\nSimonのままのほうがもっと人気出るのに！\n今のままじゃCPの時の半分も人気ないじゃん！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……CPはもう解散した。\n観客はCPに対して音楽とは関係ない部分のイメージを持ちすぎてる。\n俺はやり直したいんだ。\nただ、音楽をやれればいい。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["バーテンダー"], "content": "またそのくだらない理由ですか……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "へ～？それが解散の原因？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["バーテンダー"], "content": "はは……お嬢さん、諦めた方がいい。\nこいつは話しませんよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "お嬢さんじゃないもん！\nNEKO16歳だもん！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……そういえば、この前の猫はどうした？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "あ、今NEKOの部屋にいる……\nでもNEKOの家ペット登録してないから……\n家族も猫アレルギーだし……\n今はコッソリ飼ってるんだよね。どうしよ～～\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……飼えるやつを知ってる。\nだが、あいつはもう犬を飼ってるからな……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "ほんと！？聞いてみてくれる！？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "分かった。聞いておく。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "よかった～もうこれ以上隠し通せなくてどうしようって思ってたとこなんだ～……\nあ！じゃあiM交換しよ！\nその方が連絡とりやすいし！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ん。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imlike", "iM交換"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "いえ～！XenonのiMゲットー！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……知らないヤツに渡すなよ。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "大丈夫大丈夫！\nNEKO口硬いもん！\nXenonがSimonだってことも内緒にする！\n絶対言わない！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "今まさに言ってるだろ……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["UV_Bar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-V]"], "content": "<i>今晚表演結束！謝謝大家！</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "觀眾歡呼"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Xenon 真的太帥了！好好聽喔！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "真的～\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "啊，快沒車了，我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "嗯……NEKO 還想再待一下，Linda 醬先回去吧。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "咦？這邊等一下就要變酒吧了耶……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO 會在十二點前離開的啦。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "好吧……妳自己小心點，半夜還在外面會被無人機和執法員找碴的。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "知道知道～\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗨，牛奶。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["酒保"], "content": "好喔。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "安安！色狼先生。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……怎麼又是妳？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "什麼啊？一臉嫌棄的樣子！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……總覺得遇到妳都沒好事。\n這麼晚了還在這邊幹嘛？不怕被抓嗎？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO 是來看你表演的耶！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……咦？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "你就是 Xenon 對吧？還有！CP 的 Simon 也是你！NEKO 就想說你的臉很眼熟！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["酒保"], "content": "哈哈，又被粉絲認出來啦？就跟你說留長髮帶頭盔什麼的根本沒用了。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "少囉唆……是又怎樣？我也沒有特別要隱瞞的意思。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "哇！果然！還沒什麼人知道吧？Simon 就是 Xenon！這可是大新聞啊！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "還好吧？小聲點……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "為什麼不用 Simon 的名字繼續就好了？你的音樂會更紅的啊！現在這樣根本連 CP 一半的人氣都沒有嘛。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……CP 已經解散了，聽眾對它有太多跟音樂無關的印象。我想重新開始，單純地做音樂就好。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["酒保"], "content": "又是這個狗屁不通的理由啊……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "嘿～？這是解散的原因嗎？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["酒保"], "content": "哈哈……小妹妹，放棄吧，他不會說的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "誰是小妹妹啊！？NEKO 已經十六歲了！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……說起來，上次那隻貓，後來怎樣了？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "啊，還在 NEKO 房間裡……不過 NEKO 家沒有寵物登記，家裡也有人對貓過敏……現在完全是偷偷養著，好煩惱啊～～\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我是有認識一個人可能可以養，不過那傢伙已經養了一條狗了……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "真的嗎！？可以問問看嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "好吧，我問問看。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "得救了～不然 NEKO 已經快瞞不住家裡的人了……\n那來交換 iM 吧！比較好聯絡。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imlike", "iM 交換"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Yeah～ Xenon 的 iM GET！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……別亂傳給別人啊。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "不會不會！NEKO 很會保守祕密的啦～還有 Xenon 就是 Simon 的事情 NEKO 也不會說的！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "現在不就在說了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["UV_Bar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-V]"], "content": "<i>오늘 공연은 여기까지입니다! 감사합니다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "관중들의 환호"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Xenon 짱 멋있어! 음악도 완전 좋아!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "완전 동의!!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "아, 곧 차 끊기겠다. 어서 가자.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "음…… NEKO는 잠깐 더 있다가 갈게. Linda 짱 먼저 가봐.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "응? 여기 곧 있으면 술집으로 바뀔 텐데...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO는 12시 전에는 돌아갈 거야.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "알았어…… 조심하고! 밤늦게 바깥에 있다간 괜히 무인기나 집법원한테 트집 잡힐 수도 있으니깐.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "응~ 알았어.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Hi. 우유 한 잔 부탁해.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["바텐더"], "content": "예~\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "안녕! 변태 아저씨!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……또 너로군?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "뭐!! 완전 정색하네!?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……널 마주칠 때마다 항상 골치 아픈 일이 벌어졌던 것 같아서. 이렇게 늦은 시간에 여기서 뭐 하는 거지? 그러다 잡혀갈 수도 있다고?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "NEKO는 네 공연 보러 왔던 거라구!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "…응?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "당신이 Xenon, 맞지? 그리고! CP의 Simon도 당신이고! NEKO는 당신 얼굴 잘 기억하고 있다구!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["바텐더"], "content": "하하하. 또 팬들에게 들킨 건가? 머리를 기르든 헬멧을 쓰든 소용없을 거라고 했잖아.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "시끄러워…… 그게 뭐? 딱히 정체를 숨기려고 그렇게 한 건 아니야.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "와! 역시! 아직 다른 사람들은 모르지? Simon이 Xenon이라는 사실 말이야! 이거 완전 빅뉴스다!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "빅뉴스일 것까지야. 소리 좀 낮춰.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "왜 Simon이라는 이름을 계속 쓰지 않았던 거야? 그 이름을 썼으면 지금보다 더 유명해졌을 텐데? 지금은 CP 시절 인기의 절반도 안되잖아.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……CP는 이미 해체했다. 관중들은 이미 그 밴드에 대해 음악보다는 음악과는 무관한 다른 것들에 관심을 보이고 있어. 오직 음악만으로 평가받기 위해 혼자 다시 시작했을 뿐.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["바텐더"], "content": "참 이해 못 할 이유라니깐...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "헤~? 그래서 해체한 거야?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["바텐더"], "content": "하하……꼬마야, 포기하라고. 정확한 이유는 아마 절대 말 안 해줄 걸?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "누구보고 꼬마래!? NEKO는 벌써 16살이라구!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……그런데 저번에 그 고양이, 어떻게 됐지?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "응, 아직 NEKO 방에 있어.... 하지만 NEKO 집은 아직 애완동물 사육 허가 신청이 안 돼있어. 게다가 가족들이 다 고양이 알러지가 있어서....... 그래서 지금 안 들키게 몰래 키우려고 발악하는 중이야. 에휴, 짜증 나~\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……지인 중에 키울 수 있는 녀석이 한 명 있긴 한데... 그 녀석은 이미 개 한 마리를 키우고 있는 상황이도 하고...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "정말!? 그럼 대신 좀 물어봐 줄래?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "알았다. 물어봐 주지.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "살았다~! NEKO는 계속 몰래 키우다가 결국 들킬 것 같았거든....\n그럼 iM 교환하자! 연락도 해야 하니깐!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그래.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imlike", "iM 교환"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "Yeah～ Xenon의 iM GET!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……멋대로 다른 사람에게 퍼뜨리지 마라.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "응! 안 그럴게! NEKO는 입이 무거운 사람이라구~!  Xenon이 Simon라는 사실도 NEKO는 절대 말 안 할 거야!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "지금 대놓고 말하고 있잖아……？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["UV_Bar"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-V]"], "content": "<i>今晚表演結束！謝謝大家！</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "觀眾歡呼"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "Xenon 真的太帥了！好好聽喔！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "真的～\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "啊，快沒車了，我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Neko"], "content": "嗯……NEKO 還想再待一下，Linda 醬先回去吧。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Linda"], "content": "咦？這邊等一下就要變酒吧了耶